title: Bendigo Wholefoods
description: Carries fresh organic produce, some baked goods, vegan snacks, treats (including cake mixes) and a wide range of vegan products. Organic tea and other drinks, organic beauty products and toiletries, natural household needs (such as laundry needs), organic groceries, supplements, cookbooks and utensils, seedlings and plants, gardening tools and books, bulk foods and more.
